reviewText: This one features Lynn Vs Sheena in a sexy, competitive match. Lynn was blowing steam and took it out on Sheena. This quickly escalates into a fierce match. It didn't take long for the tops to come off, and the sexy competitors raged on. Sheena did her best here but was ultimately dominated by Lynn. I liked the spot where Lynn applied body scissors on Sheena and pinned her down to the mat. I highly recommend this one. If you enjoyed Karen Konyha Vs Heather Heist, you'll definitely love this memorable bout as well.
